{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "飞蛾行动正式发动。铁大爷以108把强弓发动第一波攻势，箭雨覆盖慕容第二、三组人马。燕冲霄逃入窄巷坐上马桶，被藏在马桶中的丝士一刀刺入要害而死。吕氏兄弟进入盛记厨房，被灶中藏身的铁条刺入小腹身亡。虎丘五杰在灯笼下放松警惕，被灯笼中破纸而出的丝士割头。程冻和郭温在棺材铺中判断失误，攻击纸扎后被棺底飞出的三条黑影刺杀。多年后一老一少讨论此战，少年推测飞蛾行动本身就是送死的圈套，慕容另有目的，最终指向三个字：楚留香。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "根据你的考证，那一次行动真的就叫做飞蛾行动?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝对不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信。",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "行动的意思是攻击，是要使仇敌毁灭。",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "飞蛾扑火，本来就是自寻死路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你难道要我相信，他们筹划这次行动，为的就是要毁灭自己?",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有这么说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你如果一定要这么想，也没有错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不懂你的意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那一次行动的真正用意，的确是让人很难想像得到的。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，铁大爷发动的第一次攻击用的是这种法子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他用的就是这种方法，用的就是普通的弓箭，只不过他在街道两旁，一共埋伏了一百零八把强弓，每人配带三十六根雕翎箭，弓箭手都是擅射'连珠'的专家，别人射出一箭时，他们已射出三箭!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁大爷和丝路先生为什么不用他们早已埋伏好的那一支奇兵?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是丝士?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点你应该能够想得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们的这一支既然已埋伏在别人绝对想像不到的隐秘之处，不到必要时，为什么要把自己暴露出来?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一类的埋伏奇兵，不到生死胜负系于一发的时候，是万万不能用的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是，我还是觉得用那些弓箭手作第一次攻势的主力，未免太弱了些。",
      "tone": "质疑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不弱。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝对不弱。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么说来，铁大爷这一次攻击完全成功了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这一个程序，主要并不是为了杀人，而是为了要让对方的阵脚动乱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当时情况，是不是这样子的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，当时的情况就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令人想不到的是，第一个落入陷阱的人，居然是燕冲霄。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的是不是那个娶了五个男伶做妾的燕子相公?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程冻冷酷谨慎，郭温机警敏捷，两人联手，所向无敌，我相信他们这一生中一定从未有过那种绝望的感觉。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信他们以后也不会有那种感觉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人是没有感觉的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以一个人活着的时候，就应该好好利用他的思想和感觉，永远不要把自己像条死鱼般吊在那里任人宰割。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点我一定会特别小心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你在想什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在想，等到灯火再亮起时，那位慕容公子带去的人还会剩下几个?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剩下的当然已不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳明秋一去之后就全无消息，慕容既不问他是否得手，也不去查明他的生死下落，就贸然带着一批人去赴约，而且居然是堂堂皇皇的走进那个根本一无所知的死镇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我认为这种做法不但愚蠢，而且可恶。谁也没有权力要别人陪他去送死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然会认为这种做法可恶，我在你这种年纪的时候，也会这么想的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你怎么想?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还记不记得他们这次行动被称为什么行动?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "飞蛾行动。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他们这次行动的目的，就像是飞蛾扑火一样，本来就是要去送死的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为这个世界上真的有这么多人想死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有这么想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想死的人为什么要去送死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们当然另外有目的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么目的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的意思并不是说他们，而是说他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们是那些去送死的人，他是要那些人去送死的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他要他们去送死，只因为他另有目的，那些不明不白就死掉的人，也许根本就不知道是怎么回事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为是怎么回事呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我认为这件事从头到尾只不过是个圈套而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "圈套?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容带那些人去送死，只不过要把自己先置之于死地而后生，让别人都认为他已经死定了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容为什么要让别人认为他已经死定了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想过很多种理由。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想来想去，到最后只剩下三个字。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三个字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪三个字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "楚留香。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    }
  ],
